{"tid":1473375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一人一信］投訴香港國際機場客運大樓走火通道被阻塞","createTime":"2019-08-14T23:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T07:54:46.000Z","uid":275866,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"636e1985c874a7d6c223565e62e9d7a93c83e76f","tid":1473375,"uid":275866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:14:39.000Z","msg":"代朋友開post<br />\n<br />\n投訴香港國際機場客運大樓走火通道被阻塞<br />\n<br />\n致香港消防處：<br />\n<br />\n本人於今天（2019年08月14日）得悉機管局就香港國際機場客運大樓實施進出管制安排（見附件一），然機管局之處理手法存有安全問題，特來函投訴。從附件二可見，圖中的逃生出口被穿上機管局制服的職員(背上標示&rdquo;TSD&rdquo;)放置鐵馬，阻塞走火通道，違反消防安全條例，作為機場使用者，本人表示相當憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n根據消防處指引，在走火通道、走廊、或樓梯堆放雜物，不單容易引致火警，發生火警時更會阻礙大家逃生，後果不堪設想，而違例者亦會被檢控，一經定罪，最高可被罰款二萬五千元。<br />\n<br />\n職員此舉全無安全意識，毋疑違反條例，更置市民和旅客安全於不顧，令人震怒。圖中亦有消防人員在旁，欲竟未有上前勸阻，實是匪夷所思，有失職之嫌。香港國際機場被譽為世界上最繁榮機場之一，竟妄顧來自世界各地乘客及機場職員的人身安全，令人失望。請 貴處馬上跟進以上事宜，以免火警發生時帶來嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n附件一：一號客運大樓運作部通告（檔案編號：T1D/040/19)<br />\n附件二：相片<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民上<br />\n<br />\n消防處聯絡方法：<br />\n電郵 : hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n熱線 : 2723 8787 <br />\n傳真 : 2311 0066<br />\n<br />\n附件一 link: <a href=\"https://extranetapps.hongkongairport.com/iwov_extra/OpenFile/T1D040-19.pdf?path=%2Fetra%2FIntranet%2FTBU%2FCircular%2FValid+Circulars+since+01+January+2005%2FT1D040-19.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fextranetapps.hongkongairport.com%2Fiwov_extra%2FOpenFile%2FT1D040-19.pdf%3Fpath%3D%252Fetra%252FIntranet%252FTBU%252FCircular%252FValid%2BCirculars%2Bsince%2B01%2BJanuary%2B2005%252FT1D040-19.pdf&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=a0943d98\" target=\"_blank\">https://extranetapps.hongkongairport.com/iwov_extra/OpenFile/T1D040-19.pdf?path=%2Fetra%2FIntranet%2FTBU%2FCircular%2FValid+Circulars+since+01+January+2005%2FT1D040-19.pdf</a><br />\n附件二 相片:<br />\nT1:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NQJqgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NQJqgp.jpg&h=db828cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbpBLgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbpBLgq.jpg&h=91b776dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emE2FPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemE2FPM.jpg&h=9fb73c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT2:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDX0suN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDX0suN.jpg&h=2be8e2a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n機場安全成疑，希望大家幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c058e59b466a116e8897d00948d915275aa7f73","tid":1473375,"uid":197404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:16:31.000Z","msg":"支持消防嚴正執法"},{"pid":"e58b23919e016f69e3c3370b72f6ddd4c215b0b0","tid":1473375,"uid":275866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:16:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"47e17099fe095fa124ae420e9d7494f723d6103d","tid":1473375,"uid":197404,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:17:10.000Z","msg":"你唔比人集會唔緊要<br />\n但你阻到人出入就唔岩"},{"pid":"2dbf0370456f6eabfea3fd004bbad213c602bb3a","tid":1473375,"uid":25048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:20:31.000Z","msg":"全球最佳機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8cf80974b55909360832679dcb97b78bf2e75d","tid":1473375,"uid":126938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:23:42.000Z","msg":"推上國際，香港機場嚴重缺乏有效之火警逃生方案！"},{"pid":"05341c19973f05f2cdc50b58c1e52ad71857eb57","tid":1473375,"uid":25048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:26:42.000Z","msg":"T1接機大堂封咗咁多條樓梯<br />\n好似連花灑系統都唔覺有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755b000871418eebb0dac5d7d10a13c9839f9f4e","tid":1473375,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:27:39.000Z","msg":"幫我推比連仔睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href